><span>.</span></p></div>\n\t\t\t</div><div class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_text et_pb_text_66  et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_bg_layout_dark\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"et_pb_text_inner\"><p><em>Du kan även ringa oss på: <a href=\"tel:+4640181100\">+46 (0) 40 181100</a></em></p></div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div><div class=\"et_pb_with_border et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column et_pb_column_106 et_animated  et_pb_css_mix_blend_mode_passthrough et-last-child\" id=\"form-link\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t<div id=\"et_pb_contact_form_2\" class=\"et_pb_module et_pb_contact_form_2 pa-contact-form-submit-fullwidth et_pb_contact_form_container clearfix\" data-form_unique_num=\"2\" data-form_unique_id=\"\" data-redirect_url=\"/tack-meddelande\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"et-pb-contact-message\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"et_pb_contact\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<form class=\"et_pb_contact_form clearfix\" method=\"post\" action=\"https://bellevuesolskydd.se/wp-json/wp/v2/pages?status=publish&#038;per_page=100&#038;page=1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"et_pb_contact_field et_pb_contact_field_12 et_pb_contact_field_half\" data-id=\"name\" data-type=\"input\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<label for=\"et_pb_contact_name_2\" class=\"et_pb_contact_form_label\">Namn</label>\n\t\t\t\t<input type=\"text\" id=\"et_pb_contact_name_2\" class=\"input\" value=\"\" name=\"et_pb_contact_name_2\" data-required_mark=\"required\" data-field_type=\"input\" data-original_id=\"name\" placeholder=\"Namn\">\n\t\t\t</p><p class=\"et_pb_contact_field et_pb_contact_field_13 et_pb_contact_field_half et_pb_contact_field_last\" data-id=\"phone\" data-type=\"input\">\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<label for=\"et_pb_contact_phone_2\" class=\"et_pb_contact_form_label\">Telefon</label>\n\t\t\t\t<input type=\"text\" id=\"et_pb_contact_phone_2\" class=\"input\" value=\"\" name=